1
00:00:00,398 --> 00:00:04,922
ظآزA little bit sorry for my love for youظآز

2
00:00:04,922 --> 00:00:10,426
ظآزSorry, I was a little lateظآز

3
00:00:10,426 --> 00:00:16,854
ظآزI really want the unconscious longing
to appear fasterظآز

4
00:00:16,854 --> 00:00:21,334
ظآزCan I get closer
and hear you say "I do" once moreظآز

5
00:00:21,334 --> 00:00:25,782
ظآزHolding hands, the scenery
in midsummer is a new journeyظآز

6
00:00:25,782 --> 00:00:30,693
ظآزThe chapters of a fairy tale
are performed one after anotherظآز

7
00:00:30,693 --> 00:00:34,742
ظآزThe promised moment
will definitely not be forgottenظآز

8
00:00:34,742 --> 00:00:39,277
ظآزCan I get closer and listen to
the frequency of your heartbeatظآز

9
00:00:39,277 --> 00:00:43,574
ظآزStart the countdown 4321,
a new sceneryظآز

10
00:00:43,574 --> 00:00:48,339
ظآزI want to see all the scenes about youظآز

11
00:00:48,339 --> 00:00:51,830
ظآزNo need to miss you anymoreظآز

12
00:00:51,830 --> 00:00:55,510
ظآزRight by your sideظآز

13
00:00:57,156 --> 00:01:00,534
=Jin Secretary=

14
00:01:00,534 --> 00:01:03,222
=Episode 21=

15
00:01:53,933 --> 00:01:54,800
Miss Jin.

16
00:01:56,933 --> 00:01:58,366
Let me get you home.

17
00:01:58,433 --> 00:02:00,966
No, you don't have to.

18
00:02:01,100 --> 00:02:02,700
I can go back by myself.

19
00:02:02,833 --> 00:02:04,500
It's not safe.

20
00:02:06,666 --> 00:02:09,066
Is there anything more dangerous
than being with you?

21
00:02:14,500 --> 00:02:17,933
I'm sorry I misremembered your birthday.

22
00:02:19,466 --> 00:02:22,000
You didn't.

23
00:02:22,066 --> 00:02:25,700
I was born ten minutes earlier than her,
but it was a day apart.

24
00:02:31,233 --> 00:02:32,192
Miss Jin.

25
00:02:34,023 --> 00:02:36,533
Miss Jin.

26
00:02:38,566 --> 00:02:39,766
I order you to get out of the car.

27
00:02:43,533 --> 00:02:48,133
It's off work time now, Mr. Lan.
You have no right to order me.

28
00:02:49,133 --> 00:02:50,400
Sir, go ahead.

29
00:02:55,900 --> 00:02:56,766
Miss Jin.

30
00:03:17,200 --> 00:03:19,833
(Why am I so mad at him?)

31
00:03:57,766 --> 00:04:02,633
Miss Jin, what's going on?

32
00:04:05,500 --> 00:04:07,008
Gosh.

33
00:04:08,133 --> 00:04:11,233
Why am I so mad at him?

34
00:04:11,300 --> 00:04:13,166
Miss, is something bothering you?

35
00:04:14,033 --> 00:04:15,296
Nothing.

36
00:04:17,333 --> 00:04:19,633
You can try this, Confidant Radio.

37
00:04:20,333 --> 00:04:22,966
You can say whatever you want to it.

38
00:04:23,466 --> 00:04:25,100
You'll feel better instantly.

39
00:04:33,066 --> 00:04:34,833
It's not my first time in love.

40
00:04:36,733 --> 00:04:39,566
Why can't I forget about you?

41
00:04:39,800 --> 00:04:44,366
You narcissistic guy.

42
00:04:48,800 --> 00:04:50,933
You're really special to me.

43
00:04:55,866 --> 00:04:57,833
But my sister also likes you.

44
00:05:01,066 --> 00:05:03,966
I'm pretending to be my sister now.

45
00:05:09,466 --> 00:05:11,166
What can I do?

46
00:05:20,266 --> 00:05:28,000
I really fell in love
with you, Lan Chen.

47
00:05:47,666 --> 00:05:49,233
Sis, you're back.

48
00:05:49,366 --> 00:05:51,733
We've been waiting for you
to celebrate birthday.

49
00:05:53,700 --> 00:05:55,166
Today is our birthdays.

50
00:05:55,266 --> 00:05:57,833
Mom and I have been waiting for you.

51
00:06:00,000 --> 00:06:00,900
Happy birthday.

52
00:06:03,366 --> 00:06:07,566
Mom, you just got out of the hospital.
Don't be too tired.

53
00:06:07,700 --> 00:06:11,500
Okay. Light the candles together.
Turn off the light.

54
00:06:17,200 --> 00:06:22,166
We always celebrate our birthdays
on this day.

55
00:06:23,700 --> 00:06:27,333
I was ten minutes earlier than you,
and yesterday was my birthday.

56
00:06:28,733 --> 00:06:30,266
Today is Xi'en's birthday.

57
00:06:32,166 --> 00:06:35,033
Why do I always celebrate my birthday
on this day?

58
00:06:37,400 --> 00:06:39,333
Xi'er, are you too tired?

59
00:06:40,900 --> 00:06:44,933
I'm fine. This job is indeed tiring.

60
00:06:45,066 --> 00:06:47,066
Xi'en, you go to work tomorrow.

61
00:06:47,066 --> 00:06:48,666
- Xi'en is still...
- Mom, I'm fine.

62
00:06:48,966 --> 00:06:51,333
I can keep awake for eight hours.

63
00:06:52,000 --> 00:06:53,300
I can go back to work.

64
00:06:54,166 --> 00:06:55,766
It's risky.

65
00:06:55,900 --> 00:06:56,766
It won't be.

66
00:07:00,066 --> 00:07:02,566
Mom, it's time for Xi'er to be herself.

67
00:07:04,133 --> 00:07:08,800
Yes, I've done so much for you,

68
00:07:10,033 --> 00:07:13,566
but you've only blamed
but never thanked me.

69
00:07:15,066 --> 00:07:16,766
Then why do I make myself so tired?

70
00:07:21,266 --> 00:07:22,333
Don't say something like that.

71
00:07:23,933 --> 00:07:26,066
Xi'er, what happened to you?

72
00:07:28,566 --> 00:07:32,633
Nothing, I'm just tired.

73
00:07:41,133 --> 00:07:45,466
Xi'en, happy birthday.

74
00:07:55,200 --> 00:07:56,733
May you be happy.

75
00:08:20,302 --> 00:08:23,552
ظآزSunk in our storyظآز

76
00:08:23,552 --> 00:08:28,325
ظآزI keep thinking of youظآز

77
00:08:30,991 --> 00:08:34,453
ظآزYou appeared and disappearedظآز

78
00:08:34,453 --> 00:08:39,023
ظآزYou once treated me so wellظآز

79
00:08:41,518 --> 00:08:45,024
ظآزThe reality has shocked meظآز

80
00:08:45,024 --> 00:08:50,420
ظآزI'm ignored by youظآز

81
00:08:50,420 --> 00:08:53,379
ظآزHow to track your tracesظآز

82
00:08:53,379 --> 00:08:58,866
ظآزI know you never really caredظآز

83
00:09:00,142 --> 00:09:02,368
ظآزA moment of awakeningظآز

84
00:09:02,368 --> 00:09:05,439
ظآزI want to escapeظآز

85
00:09:05,439 --> 00:09:07,648
ظآزLove seems like a trapظآز

86
00:09:07,648 --> 00:09:10,912
ظآزA well-designed illusionظآز

87
00:09:10,912 --> 00:09:12,960
ظآزYou're the oneظآز

88
00:09:12,960 --> 00:09:16,800
ظآزwho abandoned our pastظآز

89
00:09:16,800 --> 00:09:21,664
ظآزLet the fireworks vanish completelyظآز

90
00:09:21,664 --> 00:09:23,689
ظآزA moment of awakeningظآز

91
00:09:23,689 --> 00:09:26,606
ظآزWe repeatedly start a journeyظآز

92
00:09:26,606 --> 00:09:29,081
ظآزLove seems like a shooting starظآز

93
00:09:29,081 --> 00:09:32,320
ظآزTaking away the wishes
that never come trueظآز

94
00:09:32,320 --> 00:09:34,351
ظآزThe trace of timeظآز

95
00:09:34,351 --> 00:09:37,524
ظآزIs engraved in my fleeting memoryظآز

96
00:09:37,524 --> 00:09:40,640
ظآزAnd I indulge againظآز

97
00:10:06,382 --> 00:10:14,016
ظآزWe once watched the sunset togetherظآز

98
00:10:14,016 --> 00:10:20,672
ظآزI held your hand tightlyظآز

99
00:10:20,672 --> 00:10:26,912
ظآزWe are not the weak who fear the darkظآز

100
00:10:26,912 --> 00:10:32,192
ظآزWe're braveظآز

101
00:10:32,192 --> 00:10:35,666
ظآزThe sunset glow is projected
from the windowظآز

102
00:10:35,666 --> 00:10:36,672
Boss.

103
00:10:37,536 --> 00:10:39,387
ظآزYour colorظآز

104
00:10:39,982 --> 00:10:44,504
ظآزI pass through the crowd with youظآز

105
00:10:47,534 --> 00:10:52,495
ظآزAs if we have a tacit understanding,
attracting each otherظآز

106
00:10:55,544 --> 00:11:01,368
ظآزWhen the loneliness cracks,
warmth seeps inظآز

107
00:11:01,368 --> 00:11:08,838
ظآزYou come with light,
shining into my heartظآز

108
00:11:08,838 --> 00:11:12,319
ظآزStars fall into my eyes,
and you fall into my heartظآز

109
00:11:12,319 --> 00:11:16,440
ظآزI make a wish foolishly,
but actually, you are the shooting starظآز

110
00:11:16,440 --> 00:11:18,136
ظآزOpen my secretظآز

111
00:11:18,136 --> 00:11:24,184
ظآزI hope you find
all the tenderness hidden for youظآز

112
00:11:24,184 --> 00:11:28,056
ظآزSinking into your love,
I want to sink deeperظآز

113
00:11:28,056 --> 00:11:32,562
ظآزWith each breath,
I can feel the sweetnessظآز

114
00:11:32,562 --> 00:11:41,272
ظآزTwo lonely islands meet,
and it's the gift of fateظآز
